<p>Now&#8217;s the time to test your themes and plugins,Â and let us know if you find anything unexpected happening.Â If you think you&#8217;ve found a bug, please report it on the <a href="http://buddypress.trac.wordpress.org">BuddyPress Core Trac</a>.</p>
